# Models conventions

- Use `[JsonPropertyName("…")]` for external API shapes (Toggl snake_case / Spesnet lowercase field names).
- Local persistence (`AppSettings`, `SyncState`, `MappingsFile`) uses `ConfigService` camelCase serialization — keep property names readable C#.
- `SpesnetReferenceCache` may live inside `AppSettings`; keep `ClientsByProject` keyed by Spesnet project id.
- Per-user sync config lives under `MappingsFile.Users[togglUserId]`.
- Do not store secrets in models beyond what `AppSettings` already holds; never add secrets to committed examples.
